      <body>
         <div xml:lang="gda">
            <p n="a#1">Wy Erik meth guths nathe Danm<ex>a</ex>rks Sue<ex>r</ex>ig<ex>es</ex>
                        Norg<ex>es</ex> Wendes oc God<ex>es</ex> kony<ex>n</ex>g oc h<ex>er</ex>tugh
                        j Pome<ex>re</ex>n helsæ alla the som th<ex>e</ex>tta br<ex>e</ex>ff høra
                        ell<ex>e</ex>r see kerlege meth guth oc wo<ex>re</ex> nathe oc kungøre at
                        fore troskap oc thieniste som th<ex>e</ex>nne br<ex>e</ex>ffuiser<ex>e</ex>
                        os elskeligh <persName>Olaff Anderss<ex>on</ex>
               </persName> righet oc oss
                        h<ex>e</ex>r til trolege giort hauer oc oss oc wore kæra husfru
                                <persName>drotni<ex>n</ex>g Philippe</persName> etc. / oc wor
                        fath<ex>e</ex>rbrodh<ex>e</ex>rs h<ex>er</ex>tugh .
                                <persName>Buggislafs</persName> æchta son vm v[y] jcke selue barn
                        effter oss lade en h<ex>e</ex>r efter trolege gøra skal bothe jnnæn lands oc
                        wden lands huor vy thet aff hano[<ex>m</ex>] haue vele suo lenge han <app>
                  <lem>leuer<ex>e</ex>
                  </lem>
                  <rdg wit="#A">vel fejl for <q>leuer</q>
                  </rdg>
               </app> ♦</p>
            <p n="a#2">Tha ha[u]a vy vnt oc giue[<ex>n</ex>] honom oc hans æchta afkoma til ew[ic]h tidh
                        . frih[et] oc frelse vppa alt hans fedh<ex>e</ex>rne ok hans
                        møth<ex>e</ex>rne oc vm han noget gotz køft hau<ex>er</ex> som frelse [war]
                        t[il] foren [me]th suo dant skel at han oc hans æchta afkome scole jcke
                        afhenda ell<ex>e</ex>r selia th<ex>et</ex> gotz fran kronen suo at [kronen
                        o]k konu<ex>n</ex>gen mister syn thie[ni]ste th<ex>e</ex>r aff / ♦ Ok
                        skal han ell<ex>e</ex>r hans æchta afko<ex>m</ex>ma enc[h]te bonda gotz
                        [køpa ell<ex>e</ex>r erwa] vnder sik suo at kronen myster syn skat ok andra
                        rethzell th<ex>e</ex>r aff ♦</p>
            <p n="a#3">Thy forbiuthe vy a[lla] wor<ex>e</ex> foghe[de æm]b[i]zmen ok all[a] andra
                        hono<ex>m</ex> [e]ll<ex>e</ex>r hans æchta afkom[e] h<ex>e</ex>r wdj at
                        hindra ell<ex>e</ex>r wfor[rætæ j] nogra made vnder wor<ex>e</ex>
                        wreth[<ex>e</ex> ok] konu<ex>n</ex>glege hefnd ♦</p>
            <p n="a#4">Datum <placeName>Fl[ensburg]</placeName> anno domini mcd<hi rend="sup">o</hi>
                        sextodecimo die beati Egidii abbatis nostro sub secreto presentibus
                        [apposito] inpendenti ♦</p>
